Class PublicContribution

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Created, Distinguishable, Gildable, JsonAttribute, Votable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    Comment, Submission

    @Model(kind=ABSTRACT,
       serializer=ContributionSerializer.class)
public abstract class PublicContribution
extends Contribution
implements Distinguishable, Gildable, Votable
    This class is used to separate public contributions (submissions and comments) from private contributions (messages)
